  "subject": "Add proxy support to build msb_base",
  "commit_message": "Add proxy support to build msb_base\n\nThe process to create msb_base docker image doesn't support builds\nbehind a corporate proxy. The addition of respective support can\nbe benefitial for those developers who work inside of corporate\nnetworks.\n\nChange-Id: Id9201a7298748d2c3e1cc58b95f1516aa8b0bec0\nSigned-off-by: Victor Morales <victor.morales@intel.com>\nIssue-ID: MSB-100\n",
